data.description:
Welcome to peaceful living in our golf course community, where stylish meets comfort in this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence nestled amidst a soothing atmosphere absent of urban chaos.

The master suite is a private oasis, complete with a generously sized bedroom, a walk-in closet, and an ensuite bathroom. The three additional bedrooms provide ample space for family members or guests, each designed with comfort and style in mind.

The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and custom cabinetry to prepare a casual breakfast or host a formal dinner party.

Welcome home to a life of relaxation in our 18-hole golf course community.
